name: DareThink_01
description: The first in a series of animated gifs created with elements from my 1995 interactive animated dynamic collage, DareNotSpeakItsName. Composed from my photographs and video, as well as appropriated images, texts, sound, and dialogue from "The Wizard of Oz", gay porn videos, and news articles, DareNotSpeakItsName explored the relationship between mass-media representation, identity, imagination, and viewership as mechanisms of the closet.
